  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Game Features</h2><br>- Fully integrated first-person perspective, immersive real-life interaction——<br>The game is shot entirely in first-person perspective, allowing players to fully immerse themselves in the role of Tian Long( Main Character ), interact closely with the different beauties, and experience the emotional pulls of nightclub life in an immersive way.<br><br>- The first nightclub-themed romance simulation game——<br>The game’s theme revolves around nightclubs, a popular aspect of contemporary society, showcasing the art of flirting within nightclub culture.<br><br>- Real-life improvisation, fully on-location filming——<br>Characters in the game abandon traditional rigid scripts, letting natural dialogue development guide the narrative. This makes the interactions more realistic and provides a more immersive experience for the players. It also brings the actors closer to their roles, allowing players to understand the inner world of the actors as they play.<br><br>- Multiple heroines to pursue, multi-branching storylines——<br>In real life, choices are often singular, but in the game, players can correct past mistakes, encouraging them to embrace love boldly and passionately. The game offers multiple beauties  storylines to pursue, with personalities ranging from pure and playful to elegant, fiery, and sexy. There's always one that will catch your eye. This time, be a \"nightclub master\" and capture all the goddesses in your grasp!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Which beauty will you be mesmerised by?</h2><br>ViVi - The adorable, sweet looking beauty? <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/41f9d900bd918eba98f2451c83f72f2c.poster.avif?t=1721286029\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/41f9d900bd918eba98f2451c83f72f2c.webm?t=1721286029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/41f9d900bd918eba98f2451c83f72f2c.mp4?t=1721286029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Mia - A beauty with a love for children?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/eac226e31ad53e03ccd42ca057b49e86.poster.avif?t=1721286029\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/eac226e31ad53e03ccd42ca057b49e86.webm?t=1721286029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/eac226e31ad53e03ccd42ca057b49e86.mp4?t=1721286029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>Lily - Does the dream of a beauty aspiring to be a singer appeal to you?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/2f61437c30c73225baaa48113a2e4e83.poster.avif?t=1721286029\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/2f61437c30c73225baaa48113a2e4e83.webm?t=1721286029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/2f61437c30c73225baaa48113a2e4e83.mp4?t=1721286029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Eva - Would you mind a beauty who has experienced troubled past relationships? <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/28bc3d550a4554d8f77bdaf50a1b657a.poster.avif?t=1721286029\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/28bc3d550a4554d8f77bdaf50a1b657a.webm?t=1721286029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/28bc3d550a4554d8f77bdaf50a1b657a.mp4?t=1721286029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Ella - A beauty with a masculine heart but occasionally shows her feminine side? <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/87482298992292eb0259a4da2a4ee2c4.poster.avif?t=1721286029\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/87482298992292eb0259a4da2a4ee2c4.webm?t=1721286029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/87482298992292eb0259a4da2a4ee2c4.mp4?t=1721286029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Monica - Or a beauty who occasionally flashes a beautiful smile?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/0ffe61c7e75bb7582b80e0966f9c8d42.poster.avif?t=1721286029\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/0ffe61c7e75bb7582b80e0966f9c8d42.webm?t=1721286029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/0ffe61c7e75bb7582b80e0966f9c8d42.mp4?t=1721286029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Game Features</h2><br>- Fully integrated first-person perspective, immersive real-life interaction——<br>The game is shot entirely in first-person perspective, allowing players to fully immerse themselves in the role of Tian Long( Main Character ), interact closely with the different beauties, and experience the emotional pulls of nightclub life in an immersive way.<br><br>- The first nightclub-themed romance simulation game——<br>The game’s theme revolves around nightclubs, a popular aspect of contemporary society, showcasing the art of flirting within nightclub culture.<br><br>- Real-life improvisation, fully on-location filming——<br>Characters in the game abandon traditional rigid scripts, letting natural dialogue development guide the narrative. This makes the interactions more realistic and provides a more immersive experience for the players. It also brings the actors closer to their roles, allowing players to understand the inner world of the actors as they play.<br><br>- Multiple heroines to pursue, multi-branching storylines——<br>In real life, choices are often singular, but in the game, players can correct past mistakes, encouraging them to embrace love boldly and passionately. The game offers multiple beauties  storylines to pursue, with personalities ranging from pure and playful to elegant, fiery, and sexy. There's always one that will catch your eye. This time, be a \"nightclub master\" and capture all the goddesses in your grasp!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Which beauty will you be mesmerised by?</h2><br>ViVi - The adorable, sweet looking beauty? <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/41f9d900bd918eba98f2451c83f72f2c.poster.avif?t=1721286029\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963510/extras/41f9d900bd918eb